g.title: j4246043233
g.text: How'd you wind up here in the first place?

g.title: j4004477202
g.text: I lost the taste for serving in the Britannic army.

g.title: j1839524883
g.text: I took offense to their methodology, let's say.

g.title: j1166150260
g.text: Can you give me more than that?

g.title: j2864464451
g.text: Is that where you learned to cook square spaghetti?

g.title: j980444870
g.text: HAH! Someday, I'll live that down. Not today though, I see.

g.title: j3057795136
g.text: Well, MRE's are pretty vile, but that wasn't why I left.

g.title: j939053352
g.text: Basically, a neutral, peace-keeping organization that's supposed to deploy military units as a last resort.

g.title: j2488460917
g.text: (They make great explosives though - just don't tell Amir.)

g.title: j1828727099
g.text: That seemed to have worked out great.

g.title: j1285108980
g.text: I'd like to deploy *your* military unit. ;)

g.title: j2349709065
g.text: Can I level with you for a second, Arthur?

g.title: j4244064892
g.text: Am I pushing the wrong buttons again?

g.title: j1050620619
g.text: I get the feeling this is a touchy subject.

g.title: j1845200636
g.text: Well, if you don't want to talk, I won't make you.

g.title: j3724562986
g.text: I'm not trying to upset you.

g.title: j3718386289
g.text: Everybody has their shit. Their painful shrapnel they'd rather not dig out.

g.title: j2480898170
g.text: You've been curious for a while about my army life. Why?

g.title: j408971164
g.text: Why're you asking about my army life?

g.title: j2634092320
g.text: I'm just trying to get to know you. Really, I am.

g.title: j1030210730
g.text: Sheesh, sorry. Just trying to have a conversation.

g.title: j2624805361
g.text: I'm just trying to get to know you more.

g.title: j1242803851
g.text: And I'm doing this because I want to be a better friend.

g.title: j2977889768
g.text: And I'm doing this because I care about you.

g.title: j2755504903
g.text: Try chatting about the weather next time.

g.title: j4206552322
g.text: I'm trying to get to know you better.

g.title: j2126602108
g.text: So, if this isn't the right way to go about it, I'm sorry.

g.title: j385138007
g.text: So, I'm sorry if I'm bothering you.

g.title: j1922613458
g.text: Well, next time maybe go for the weather.

g.title: j3678802630
g.text: I just want to know what made Arthur, *Arthur.*

g.title: j2356839581
g.text: I just want to know what made Arthur, *Arthur.*

g.title: j1197499193
g.text: I know. And I'm not mad. I'm just not ready to spill, yet. Another time.

g.title: j1479049561
g.text: Well. I suppose if you're willing to stand around put up with me...

g.title: j662875640
g.text: It's not a story I like telling.

g.title: j1308765282
g.text: I know you're not trying to be rude. Or pry for the sake of it.

g.title: j3036759601
g.text: Because I haven't been able to stop thinking about you since I've shown up here.

g.title: j3523360089
g.text: But...fine. You've been a good sport. I'll give you an inch.

g.title: j3426786992
g.text: But digging out my painful shrapnel isn't exactly a pleasant conversation.

g.title: j737054874
g.text: All right. Fine. What do you want to know?

g.title: j318624860
g.text: What do you want to know?

g.title: j691852311
g.text: I get it. I'll back off.

g.title: j1189762495
g.text: I didn't realize the stories I was asking for were painful.

g.title: j1003187149
g.text: I know, and I still owe you that rain check.

g.title: j3920087284
g.text: Why did you quit the Brittanic army?

g.title: j2229402730
g.text: No. It's fine. I'm not saying you can't ask. I'm just saying I might not want to tell you the answers just yet.

g.title: j1412436086
g.text: I'm just not the kind of man who rushes into these kinds of things -

g.title: j1746198808
g.text: Relationships, or digging out painful shrapnel from my past.

g.title: j456493809
g.text: So you might just have to be patient. Or stubborn.

g.title: j4035210930
g.text: When you enlist, you enlist to serve.

g.title: j3353416163
g.text: you tend to do it for a reason.

g.title: j1278071931
g.text: Something tells me you might have those qualities, however.

g.title: j2470284010
g.text: Heh. That explains why you're so bloody nosy, I suppose.

g.title: j2288450791
g.text: Your Prince. Your Country. Your brothers & sisters in arms.

g.title: j167409212
g.text: Some people do it because they have nowhere else to go.

g.title: j70854721
g.text: Look, I'm just not the kind of man who jumps into these kinds of things.

g.title: j763265584
g.text: And the innocents you're meant to be protecting in the first place.

g.title: j269340831
g.text: Some for glory. Some for power. Some to feed the voice in their heads that says "kill."

g.title: j1989732863
g.text: Relationships, or painful stories about my past.

g.title: j312136084
g.text: But a funny thing happens, when people get into positions of power. The higher you go, the smaller people look.

g.title: j379054114
g.text: Some are idiots who do it to be noble. To protect. To be heroes. Like me.

g.title: j2132715816
g.text: And if you don't want to be standing around waiting for me? I get it.

g.title: j934122168
g.text: I didn't realize the stories I was asking for were painful.

g.title: j2043394258
g.text: The more people look less like themselves, and more like...dots.

g.title: j755898242
g.text: I figured the ICR might be a better place to scratch that itch than His Majesty's Royal Army.

g.title: j3726254958
g.text: Sol knows that won't be the first time that's happened.

g.title: j1607527139
g.text: It's fine. Everybody has their shit.

g.title: j383231971
g.text: Thanks. I'm sure we'll get there. Just...not today.

g.title: j3589876764
g.text: Like numbers on a piece of paper. Like incidentals.

g.title: j2127653769
g.text: But it was just more of the same.

g.title: j1320161046
g.text: I can't imagine why. You're so approachable and talkative.

g.title: j1994219576
g.text: I got real bloody sick of it.

g.title: j3746427058
g.text: I get the feeling there's more to it than that.

g.title: j1593460943
g.text: On what? The soldier stories or the whole "I have feelings for you" thing?

g.title: j3238031131
g.text: Today, at any rate. Not nearly drunk enough for the rest.

g.title: j3190462851
g.text: You don't like to give up an inch, do you?

g.title: j3107991886
g.text: I appreciate what you did share.

g.title: j614054799
g.text: Heh. Won't say no to free beer.
